                            <comment id="15069813" author="githubbot" created="Wed, 23 Dec 2015 16:16:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user StephanEwen commented on the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1474#issuecomment-166934557&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1474#issuecomment-166934557&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    As some context: The class does not lock on all calls that can modify the state of the buffers (such as every `write()` call, for performance), so the locking removed in this PR becomes not effective anyways.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    +1, will merge this...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
